Find:

nginx
Copy
Edit
PasswordAuthentication no
Change it to:

nginx
Copy
Edit
PasswordAuthentication yes
Save and exit (Ctrl+X, then Y, then Enter)

Restart SSH:

bash
Copy
Edit
sudo systemctl restart ssh
